{"tid":1778500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"平靜嘅時候應該做啲咩？","createTime":"2019-12-11T04:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T11:00:42.000Z","uid":107092,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"44ecd6062a207b64382b71fb96724e923196cf75","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"1. 思想Full Gear<br />\n<ins>政治類</ins><br />\n好多6月先覺醒嘅朋友其實對社運或者政治都係認識尚淺，<br />\n甚至認為經常掛係嘴邊嘅民主只係純粹少數服從多數。<br />\n建議可以多睇下文章，唔鍾意睇文章嘅可以YouTube搵啲片聽下。<br />\n至少要對香港嘅體制、社運嘅歷史、唔同政治人物做過啲乜有基本認識，<br />\n日後嘅社運討論先會高質。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>抗爭類</ins><br />\n被捕須知、戰術企位、魔法調配、物資選購；<br />\n就算自己唔會用到都可以睇下，<br />\n到時落到場自己唔用都可以幫其他人手。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>思想類</ins><br />\n基本嘅社運思維，例如不分化不割席不捉鬼依啲一定要常駐，<br />\n連登仔已經捉錯好多次鬼，<br />\n屠妖又係鬼，起到批槍又係鬼，<br />\n可見連登仔根本冇將依啲放係心。<br />\n<br />\n另外就係邏輯，<br />\n經常保持好邏輯思維再配搭思想嘅FullGear先唔會咁易被煽動。<br />\n另外好多藍絲以為自己講嘢好有道理其實都係充滿邏輯漏洞，<br />\n聽得出佢嘅錯誤嘅時候，其實唔洗反駁佢，<br />\n指出佢嘅邏輯錯誤已經可以收佢皮，<br />\n或者可以套翻佢嘅邏輯反攻返佢。<br />\n<br />\n2. 必須訓練體能<br />\n訓練體能無分和勇，相信大家都知道就算係和理非，<br />\n跑慢幾步都會入去48個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n3. 訓練身手<br />\n講緊嘅係翻欄杆，爬石駁依啲，<br />\n重要性我諗都唔洗多講<br />\n求其搵條欄杆，<br />\n驚樣衰嘅可以去行人隧道冇咁開揚，<br />\n入去左翻右翻。<br />\n<br />\n4. Twitter 戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwiq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=22299ca3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n搭車禁幾下，返工禁幾下，<br />\n有意義過係IG share啲刪一貼百嘅post。"},{"pid":"30f1f36ebaa66a7088c389386039cbc3daa35a79","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"認同請幫推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7874935de29a561be8b59f679dad22164357ecdb","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:16:13.000Z","msg":"純粹比咗啲方向，<br />\n具體要睇啲乜做啲乜都係要靠大家自己去search。"},{"pid":"00b279552369529ff6761e5af10b6541d3d51cde","tid":1778500,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:17:09.000Z","msg":"做宣傳！做滲透！"},{"pid":"bb69b4d28e79610ee3293723744c7218aed92774","tid":1778500,"uid":343431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"做運動，做文宣，自學<br />\n<br />\n有心就大把野搞"},{"pid":"cad5c22a10f386c93373014bb52c6bb92cfd26a6","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:17:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb8d1e9f7c4c008c913f3a6c6c46ef58839e7df6","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb69b4d28e79610ee3293723744c7218aed92774","tid":1778500,"uid":343431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"做運動，做文宣，自學<br />\n<br />\n有心就大把野搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:18:14.000Z","msg":"腦袋Full Gear，思想Be Water。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb06d39f3340c1435f3becaa486dd66812a0f462","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:18:27.000Z","msg":"腦袋Full Gear，思想Be Water。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1741816d910105f7360771b06b476d83bd4d4930","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"腦袋Full Gear，思想Be Water。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4e2cae7a10e068d60b7ba51ac3a11b5a271519","tid":1778500,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1741816d910105f7360771b06b476d83bd4d4930","tid":1778500,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"腦袋Full Gear，思想Be Water。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"Heart on fire,brain be water"},{"pid":"ee01661f812bbb606537e3a8b2637d04a4b133da","tid":1778500,"uid":